.TH "snd_hdac_stream_setup_periods" 9 "snd_hdac_stream_setup_periods" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snd_hdac_stream_setup_periods \- set up BDL entries
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" snd_hdac_stream_setup_periods
.BI "(struct hdac_stream *azx_dev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "azx_dev" 12
HD-audio core stream to set up
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Set up the buffer descriptor table of the given stream based on the
period and buffer sizes of the assigned PCM substream.
